@startuml Level 0 DFD - Bus Station Management System (Context Diagram)

' NOTE: Gane-Sarson Level 0 has EXTERNAL ENTITIES (squares) + ONE PROCESS (rounded rect).
' PlantUML: we use plain rectangles for both; roundcorner would make everything rounded
' (external entities would look like processes), so we keep square corners.

skinparam maxwidth 1600
skinparam maxheight 1100
skinparam dpi 300
scale max 1600x1100

title Level 0 Data Flow Diagram - Bus Station Management System (Context Diagram)\n(Gane-Sarson style: squares = external entities, one box = process)

' External entities (Gane-Sarson: squares â€” sources/sinks of data, NOT processes)
rectangle "Passenger" as Passenger
rectangle "Staff" as Staff
rectangle "Payment Gateway" as PaymentGateway
rectangle "GPS Service" as GPSService
rectangle "Communication Service" as CommService
rectangle "Management" as Management
rectangle "Maintenance Provider" as MaintenanceProvider

' Single process (Gane-Sarson: rounded rectangle = the system as one process)
rectangle "0.0\nBus Station\nManagement System" as System

' Data flows
Passenger --> System : Booking requests
System --> Passenger : Tickets, confirmations

Staff --> System : Operations input
System --> Staff : Booking and trip information

PaymentGateway --> System : Payment status
System --> PaymentGateway : Payment requests

GPSService --> System : Location data
System --> GPSService : Tracking requests

CommService --> System : Delivery status
System --> CommService : Notification requests

Management --> System : Report and policy requests
System --> Management : Reports, analytics

MaintenanceProvider --> System : Maintenance reports
System --> MaintenanceProvider : Maintenance schedule

@enduml
